Koleka 50 fosses communes (mabulu ya nkunda na nzoto ya bato ebele esika moko) emonani na mboka ya Yumbi, na Maï-Ndombe,  elobi ONU. 
 "Ezali na pene na 50 mabulu too nkunda ya bato ebele to mpe moko moko oyo tomoni" na Yumbi, eyebisi Abdoul Aziz Thioye, directeur ya Bureau conjoint ya ONU ya makoki ya bomoto na RDC (BCNUDH).





 


